item.title: About me
item.author: cosmo.marce <at> gmail <dot> com (Marcela Sena)
item.description: This is me My name is Marcela Sena and I’m from Tepic in Nayarit, Mexico. I currently live and work in Guadalajara, Jalisco. I’m a Software Engineer passionate for programming, learn new stuffs, diversity in IT, movies, music, anime, running, hiking and my dog; her name is Frida like the mexican painter Frida Kahlo. I love rainy afternoons and a delicious cup of coffee in the morning with a piece of sweet bread (my favorite is the cappuccino).
